    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You just used the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.zJ3Jakto3oqJTLZR]{Limit Break} action.</p><p><strong>Area</strong> @Template[type:emanation|distance:20]</p><p><strong>Duration</strong> [[@actor.flags.pf2e.limit-rank]] rounds</p><hr /><p>Your peerless defense ensures that your allies will not fall or falter while they stand by you. While within your emanation, you and your allies cannot fall below 1 hit point. Allies that are at 0 hit points and currently dying are automatically stabilised by the emanation, even if they are no longer within it.</p><p>When Last Bastion expires, all allies within the emanation at the time of expiry gain temporary hitpoints equal to half their total hit points which last for 2 rounds.</p>",
